extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Express Games], an online store where you can purchase your favorite retro games.

  h1 Dynamic Content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else 
    p The store has the following record counts:

    ul 
      li #[strong Games:] !{data.game_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.game_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.game_instance_available_count}
      li #[strong Consoles:] !{data.console_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}